{
  "message": "feat(fuzz): extend broadcast_shapes corpus with 14 edge-case seeds\n\nNew seeds covering:\n- Zero dimensions in various positions (first, second, multiple)\n- High-rank arrays (6D, 7D)\n- Broadcast positions (start, middle, end)\n- Incompatible shapes for error path coverage\n- Large 2-byte dimension encoding\n- Single-element arrays\n- Cross-rank broadcasting (3D vs 1D, 4D vs 2D)\n- All-dimensions-need-broadcast scenario\n\nBrings corpus from 14 to 28 seeds.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
